5
6 A Joint Resolution approving certain proposed
permanent rules of the Oklahoma Health Care
7 Authority; and directing distribution.
8
9
10 WHEREAS, pursuant to Section 308 of Title 75 of the Oklahoma
11 Statutes, major rules shall be addressed in a joint resolution only
12 addressing major rules; and
13 WHEREAS, the proposed permanent rules in Oklahoma Health Care
14 Authority OAC 317:30-3-57, 317:30-3-59, 317:30-5-2, 317:30-5-9,
15 317:30-5-10, 317:30-5-11, 317:30-5-15, 317:30-5-42.4, 317:30-5-261,
16 317:30-5-361, and 317:30-5-431 meet the definition of major rule set
17 forth in Section 250.3 of Title 75 of the Oklahoma Statutes.
18 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE AND THE HOUSE OF
19 REPRESENTATIVES OF THE 2ND SESSION OF THE 60TH OKLAHOMA LEGISLATURE:
20 SECTION 1. The following proposed permanent rules promulgated
21 by the Oklahoma Health Care Authority are hereby approved: OAC
22 317:30-3-57, 317:30-3-59, 317:30-5-2, 317:30-5-9, 317:30-5-10,
23 317:30-5-11, 317:30-5-15, 317:30-5-42.4, 317:30-5-261, 317:30-5-361,
24 and 317:30-5-431.
